    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute definition of showroom quality, preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains free of swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the hand-stitched leather remains supple and matte, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still carries that distinct factory aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced navigation interface, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Non-smoker owned, no pets, and zero accidents.",
      "price": 48500.0,
